 197:Generated_Source\PSoC4/cyfitter_cfg.c **** * Summary:
 198:Generated_Source\PSoC4/cyfitter_cfg.c **** *   Performs the initialization of all of the clocks in the device based on the
 199:Generated_Source\PSoC4/cyfitter_cfg.c **** *   settings in the Clock tab of the DWR.  This includes enabling the requested
